<p>Using only <span class="abbreviation">PID<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Proportional Integral Derivative"></template></span> will race to the target, so you can get really fast and not well controlled acceleration. Motion Magic will accelerate, cruise, and then decelerate.</p>
